---
title: Speedy Hamburger Chorizo Quesadillas with Pickles and Special Sauce
description: This dinner has all the vibes of a chorizo cheeseburger dinner, as a quesadilla! Paired up with dill pickles and roasted sweet potatoes, it'll be a new family fave.
